<plot>Jerry, who has been having an affair with his secretary, Monica, wants out of his marriage to wife Adrianna. But he and his business partner, Paul, doesn't want the soon-to-be "ex" to get her hands onto their company assets. So Paul puts a bug in Jerry's ear - get Matt, one of their employees to seduce the wife, then have a P.I. named Simms collect proof of the affair. All seems to be going according to plan ... until Jerry discovers he is actually feeling jealous and wants his wife back.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?425514</url></doc>
